(122, 1, '2026-01-21 18:06:01', '2026-01-21 18:06:01', 'Experience the taste of Algerian heritage. Our Royal Chorba Frik is prepared using traditional clay pots to preserve the deep, smoky flavor of the cracked wheat. We use only premium lamb shoulder and a blend of \"Ras El Hanout\" specially sourced from Biskra. Served with a side of house-made lemon-infused sourdough and fresh mint. 100% Halal.', 'Royal Saffron Chorba Frik', 'A sophisticated take on the traditional Algerian soup. Cracked green wheat simmered for 6 hours with tender lamb medallions, infused with authentic saffron threads and fresh coriander.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'royal-saffron-chorba-frik', '', '', '2026-01-21 18:06:01', '2026-01-21 18:06:01', '', 0, 'http://127.0.0.1/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=122', 0, 'product', '', 0),
