(124, 1, '2026-01-21 18:14:45', '2026-01-21 18:14:45', '<p data-path-to-node=\"8,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"8,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">The Heritage of Algiers on a Plate.</b></p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8,1\">Our Signature Royal Couscous is the embodiment of Algerian hospitality. Every grain of semolina is hand-rolled by our master artisans and steamed three times over an aromatic vapor to achieve a cloud-like lightness, then delicately finished with organic clarified butter.</p>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8,2\"><b data-path-to-node=\"8,2\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">The Trilogy of Meats:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<ul data-path-to-node=\"8,3\">\r\n 	<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8,3,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"8,3,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Agneau de Lait:</b> A tender milk-fed lamb shank, braised for seven hours until it falls from the bone.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8,3,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"8,3,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Coquelet au Safran:</b> Roasted free-range spring chicken infused with premium Taliouine saffron.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8,3,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"8,3,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Merguez Artisanale:</b> Hand-spiced beef sausages, prepared daily with our secret blend of Saharan spices.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-path-to-node=\"8,4\">Served with a refined garden of honey-glazed root vegetables and buttery chickpeas. This dish is presented in a ceremonial hand-painted Gassa, offering a true royal feast that honors the soul of Algerian gastronomy.</p>', 'Couscous Royal à l\'Algéroise', 'A majestic symphony of textures and heritage. Hand-rolled artisan semolina served with a trilogy of premium Halal meats, slow-simmered in a saffron-infused red velvet broth.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'couscous-royal-a-lalgeroise', '', '', '2026-01-21 18:16:22', '2026-01-21 18:16:22', '', 0, 'http://127.0.0.1/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=124', 0, 'product', '', 0),
