(126, 1, '2026-01-21 18:21:11', '2026-01-21 18:21:11', 'A jewel of Algerian tradition, this dish is a sophisticated celebration of refinement. We select the finest Halal lamb, braised slowly until it reaches a butter-like consistency within a delicate reduction of pure honey and cinnamon. The sauce is scented with the essence of orange blossoms and carries the rich sweetness of plump apricots and premium prunes. To finish, the dish is adorned with a generous scattering of toasted Marcona almonds, offering a fragrant journey through the history of the Maghreb.', 'L’Or Noir: Tajine Lahlou Royal', 'An exquisite masterpiece of sweet and savory harmony. Slow-poached golden fruits and tender lamb medallions simmered in a shimmering orange-blossom honey nectar.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'lor-noir-tajine-lahlou-royal', '', '', '2026-01-21 18:21:11', '2026-01-21 18:21:11', '', 0, 'http://127.0.0.1/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=126', 0, 'product', '', 0),
