(128, 1, '2026-01-21 18:24:21', '2026-01-21 18:24:21', 'These select lamb chops represent the soul of the Casbah\'s grilling tradition. Each cut is marinated for twenty-four hours in a refined mixture of cold-pressed olive oil, fresh garlic, and traditional \"Ras El Hanout\" spices. Grilled to order over open flames, the meat remains incredibly tender with a delicate charred exterior. Served alongside a light saffron rice and a cooling herb-infused yogurt, this dish offers a perfect balance of rustic fire and royal elegance.', 'Côtelettes d’Agneau au Charbon', '<p data-path-to-node=\"5\">Premium lamb chops marinated in a signature blend of Saharan spices and grilled over natural wood charcoal for a deep, authentic smoky flavor.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 data-path-to-node=\"6\"></h4>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'cotelettes-dagneau-au-charbon', '', '', '2026-01-21 18:24:21', '2026-01-21 18:24:21', '', 0, 'http://127.0.0.1/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=128', 0, 'product', '', 0),
