(130, 1, '2026-01-21 18:26:35', '2026-01-21 18:26:35', 'A masterpiece of Algerian pastry art, these Dziriettes are crafted using centuries-old techniques from the capital. The thin, translucent dough is hand-pleated to form a nest for a rich filling of local blanched almonds, organic lemon zest, and natural vanilla. After a light golden bake, each pastry is bathed in a warm orange-blossom honey syrup, creating a moist, fragrant interior with a slight crunch. These jewels are the perfect companion to a glass of fresh mint tea.', 'Dziriettes à l\'Amande Royale', 'Traditional Algiers tea cakes, hand-sculpted into delicate flower shapes and filled with premium ground almonds and citrus zest, finished with a drizzle of pure honey.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'dziriettes-a-lamande-royale', '', '', '2026-01-21 18:26:35', '2026-01-21 18:26:35', '', 0, 'http://127.0.0.1/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=130', 0, 'product', '', 0),
