(132, 1, '2026-01-21 18:29:15', '2026-01-21 18:29:15', 'This refined version of the classic Algerian Bourek elevates traditional street food to a royal standard. We use paper-thin \"dioul\" pastry, filled with premium minced lamb sautéed with caramelized onions, fresh parsley, and a signature blend of warm spices. Each parcel is flash-fried to a perfect golden crisp and served with a wedge of fresh lemon and a sprig of watercress. The result is a light yet flavorful start to a luxury meal, offering a satisfying crunch with every bite.', 'Bourek Royal à la Viande', 'Delicate, crispy pastry leaves hand-folded around a savory filling of spiced Halal lamb, fresh herbs, and a hint of melted gruyère.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'bourek-royal-a-la-viande', '', '', '2026-01-21 18:29:15', '2026-01-21 18:29:15', '', 0, 'http://127.0.0.1/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=132', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(133, 1, '2026-01-21 18:29:05', '2026-01-21 18:29:05', '', 'moh-6', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'moh-6', '', '', '2026-01-21 18:29:05', '2026-01-21 18:29:05', '', 132, 'http://127.0.0.1/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/moh-6.png', 0, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(134, 1, '2026-01-21 18:31:08', '2026-01-21 18:31:08', 'This refined white couscous is a testament to the subtle side of Algerian royalty. The semolina is steamed to a pearl-like finish and lightly scented with a hint of cinnamon and clarified butter. Unlike the red version, this dish focuses on the purity of flavors, featuring tender chunks of premium Halal lamb that have been simmered until they melt. It is garnished with \"Tfaya\"—a sophisticated mixture of caramelized onions and golden raisins—and toasted chickpeas, providing a gentle sweetness that perfectly complements the savory meat.', 'Couscous Blanc Perlé à l\'Agneau', '<p data-path-to-node=\"5\">A delicate, snow-white couscous steamed with aromatic cinnamon and topped with succulent slow-cooked lamb and a medley of sweet caramelized onions.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 data-path-to-node=\"6\"></h4>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'couscous-blanc-perle-a-lagneau', '', '', '2026-01-21 18:31:08', '2026-01-21 18:31:08', '', 0, 'http://127.0.0.1/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=134', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(135, 1, '2026-01-21 18:31:04', '2026-01-21 18:31:04', '', 'moh-7', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'moh-7', '', '', '2026-01-21 18:31:04', '2026-01-21 18:31:04', '', 134, 'http://127.0.0.1/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/moh-7.png', 0, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(136, 1, '2026-01-21 18:32:54', '2026-01-21 18:32:54', 'This prestigious version of Tajine Zitoun is a study in savory balance. We use select cuts of milk-fed veal, slow-cooked in a traditional clay pot until the meat is exceptionally tender. The sauce is built on a foundation of caramelized onions and aromatic herbs, enriched with the bright, salty notes of premium green olives and sweet garden carrots. A touch of saffron provides a golden hue and a subtle floral depth, while a final squeeze of fresh lemon juice lifts the flavors. Served with traditional crusty bread to capture every drop of the rich, reduced jus.', 'Tajine Zitoun à la Moelle', 'A refined Algiers classic featuring tender braised veal and cracked green olives simmered in a velvety saffron and thyme-scented sauce.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'tajine-zitoun-a-la-moelle', '', '', '2026-01-21 18:32:54', '2026-01-21 18:32:54', '', 0, 'http://127.0.0.1/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=136', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(137, 1, '2026-01-21 18:31:45', '2026-01-21 18:31:45', '', 'moh-8', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'moh-8', '', '', '2026-01-21 18:31:45', '2026-01-21 18:31:45', '', 136, 'http://127.0.0.1/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/moh-8.png', 0, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(138, 1, '2026-01-21 18:34:36', '2026-01-21 18:34:36', 'A tribute to the rich waters of the Algerian coast, these jumbo prawns are selected for their impressive size and sweet, lobster-like flavor. Each prawn is split and grilled to perfection over high heat, ensuring a delicate char while keeping the interior succulent. They are finished with a house-made Chermoula—a traditional blend of cold-pressed olive oil, fresh coriander, and toasted cumin—and served with a side of spicy Harissa-infused dip. This dish offers a sophisticated, lighter alternative to red meat, bringing the fresh essence of the Mediterranean directly to your table.', 'Crevettes Royales à la Plancha', '<p data-path-to-node=\"5\">Colossal Mediterranean tiger prawns, flame-grilled and brushed with a vibrant garlic and parsley \"Chermoula\" marinade, served with a charred lemon zest.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 data-path-to-node=\"6\"></h4>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'crevettes-royales-a-la-plancha', '', '', '2026-01-21 18:34:37', '2026-01-21 18:34:37', '', 0, 'http://127.0.0.1/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=138', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(139, 1, '2026-01-21 18:33:27', '2026-01-21 18:33:27', '', 'moh-9', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'moh-9', '', '', '2026-01-21 18:33:27', '2026-01-21 18:33:27', '', 138, 'http://127.0.0.1/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/moh-9.png', 0, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(140, 1, '2026-01-21 18:36:46', '2026-01-21 18:36:46', 'The Algerian Baklawa is a masterpiece of patience and skill. Unlike other versions, ours uses no filo dough; instead, our pastry chefs hand-roll twelve translucent layers of dough to achieve a uniquely delicate crunch. The heart of the pastry is a generous filling of premium crushed almonds and walnuts, lightly spiced with cinnamon. Once baked to a shimmering golden hue, it is bathed in organic honey, allowing the flavors to meld into a rich, floral sweetness. Each diamond-shaped piece is a jewel of Algiers\' Ottoman heritage.', 'Baklawa Algéroise au Miel Pur', '<p data-path-to-node=\"5\">Multiple layers of hand-stretched, paper-thin pastry filled with a rich blend of roasted almonds and walnuts, scented with orange blossom and drenched in pure mountain honey.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 data-path-to-node=\"6\"></h4>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'baklawa-algeroise-au-miel-pur', '', '', '2026-01-21 18:36:47', '2026-01-21 18:36:47', '', 0, 'http://127.0.0.1/wordpress/?post_type=product&#038;p=140', 0, 'product', '', 0),
